    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is caused by the `multiple_values = true` dervie attribute for `constructor_args`. As the [doc](https://docs.rs/clap/latest/clap/struct.Arg.html#method.multiple_values) says, there's no more  options allowed to follow `--construct-args`. That is to say the `--contructor-args` option must be the last one for the cmd line.",
